                <p>
                    The QLTalk ("Quartiz Leto Talk") addon has been developed to enable members of La Danse Macabre to talk
                    to each other regardless on which character, realm or faction they are. If you are on your Alliance character
                    and you want to talk with your fellow guildies, this is the addon you are looking for.
                </p>

                <p><b>How to use the addon?</b></p>

                <p>
                    To use the addon you can simply use the "/ql" command to send a message to your fellow guildies.
                </p>

                <p>
                    If you type:
                </p>

                <p>
                    <code>/ql hello everyone, how are we doing</code>
                </p>

                <p>
                    it will send the message "hello everyone, how are we doing" to everyone in the guild. You can of course also use the
                    chat window.
                </p>

                <p><b>How to install the addon?</b></p>

